T-DOSE is a free and yearly event held in The Netherlands to promote use and development of Open Source Software. During this event Open Source projects, developers and visitors can exchange ideas and knowledge. This years event was held on 26 and 27 October 2013 at the Fontys University of Applied Science in Eindhoven.

Info at:
http://www.t-dose.org
